column2: Sunny scattered clouds no wind. no boats.  Rain weeks ago. 1 seagull.
Clear very breezy dry. no boats.
Breezy warm. 3 ski boats 1 sail boat 2 motor boats 1 canoe.
Cloudless sky this morning. One adult eagle and eaglet watching from their nesting area.  Loons could be heard from Lower Springstead Lake. They did not incubate their eggs this spring.

Air temperature 60 degrees.  Sunny morning with light breeze causing ripples across water.  Observed one adult eagle perched high close to its nest.  Did not see the young eaglet that was born this spring.
